Problem name: Sample Coq proof

Description:

This is a sample coq proof

Function signature: Inductive day : Type :=,| monday,| tuesday,| wednesday,| thursday,| friday,| saturday,| sunday.,Definition next_weekday (d: day) : day :=, match d with, | monday => tuesday, | tuesday => wednesday, | wednesday => thursday, | thursday => friday, | friday => monday, | saturday => monday, | sunday => monday, end.,Example test_next_weekday:, (next_weekday (next_weekday saturday)) = tuesday.
